00:13:17,240 --> 00:13:19,480
I say it's not enough.

296
00:13:23,040 --> 00:13:24,520
This is a foreigner.

297
00:13:26,720 --> 00:13:28,720
I'm not good at drawing foreigners' portraits.

298
00:13:29,000 --> 00:13:30,280
Supervisor Cao can't explain it.

299
00:13:30,840 --> 00:13:32,840
I can only draw like this.

300
00:13:33,280 --> 00:13:34,960
Foreigners do look alike.

301
00:13:35,560 --> 00:13:36,360
I can't recognize them either.

302
00:13:37,560 --> 00:13:39,120
But who is that young master?

303
00:13:39,840 --> 00:13:41,880
He turned his back to Steward Cao.

304
00:13:42,360 --> 00:13:43,320
He said he didn't see it clearly.

305
00:13:45,920 --> 00:13:48,840
Is your son with the Westerners?

306
00:13:49,080 --> 00:13:49,760
Or

307
00:13:50,320 --> 00:13:51,560
he's from the Association?

308
00:13:52,800 --> 00:13:53,840
Supervisor Cao said

309
00:13:54,080 --> 00:13:55,320
Geng Ruilin was very respectful to him.

310
00:13:56,200 --> 00:13:58,360
That foreigner is on the same level with him.

311
00:14:01,640 --> 00:14:02,720
Your son.

312
00:14:03,840 --> 00:14:05,160
The Six Association.

313
00:14:07,520 --> 00:14:08,400
The man

314
00:14:09,040 --> 00:14:10,920
with Wuqi

315
00:14:11,160 --> 00:14:12,000
is also a noble man.

316
00:14:12,200 --> 00:14:13,720
The serial killer of the face-cutting case

317
00:14:17,520 --> 00:14:18,960
[He finally appeared again.]

318
00:14:20,240 --> 00:14:21,520
I must catch him this time.

319
00:14:22,840 --> 00:14:24,000
Geng Rulin and this foreigner

320
00:14:24,600 --> 00:14:25,520
must know his identity.

321
00:14:26,840 --> 00:14:27,920
Shencheng Police Station

322
00:14:28,600 --> 00:14:29,800
has no right to enforce the law.

323
00:14:30,720 --> 00:14:32,560
So we can only start with Geng Ruilin.

324
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:34,400
Then your son and the Westerners

325
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:36,080
will be caught sooner or later.

326
00:14:36,920 --> 00:14:38,400
If this foreigner

327
00:14:39,040 --> 00:14:40,280
is a businessman,

328
00:14:41,440 --> 00:14:43,640
Wenxuan might know something.

329
00:14:44,680 --> 00:14:46,520
I'll investigate Geng Ruilin's whereabouts first.

330
00:14:46,920 --> 00:14:48,040
Let’s split up.

331
00:14:53,360 --> 00:14:53,760
Coming.

332
00:14:54,440 --> 00:14:54,960
Let's go in.

333
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,960
Where is

334
00:14:56,960 --> 00:14:59,520
Where's your sweet secretary?

335
00:15:00,520 --> 00:15:01,240
Young Master's friend?

336
00:15:01,800 --> 00:15:03,640
Why would a servant like him ask?

337
00:15:03,760 --> 00:15:04,640
My Young Master's schedule...

338
00:15:04,800 --> 00:15:06,360
my Young Master's schedule.

339
00:15:08,320 --> 00:15:09,600
You know what happened that day?

340
00:15:09,720 --> 00:15:10,160
Of course.

341
00:15:10,920 --> 00:15:11,680
After you got angry,

342
00:15:12,120 --> 00:15:13,880
I figured out the whole story.

343
00:15:14,440 --> 00:15:14,920
And

344
00:15:15,400 --> 00:15:17,160
I also asked all the servants of the Ji family

345
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,720
to tell me immediately

346
00:15:19,000 --> 00:15:20,080
you must tell me immediately.

347
00:15:20,560 --> 00:15:21,880
I'll come out to welcome him.

348
00:15:22,720 --> 00:15:24,880
You don't have to be so formal.

349
00:15:25,080 --> 00:15:26,360
I'm no longer angry.

350
00:15:26,640 --> 00:15:27,080
Let's go.

351
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:41,840
Have a seat.

352
00:15:44,800 --> 00:15:45,960
By the way, I wanted to ask you.

353
00:15:46,520 --> 00:15:47,960
Didn't we agree to go to your house for class?

354
00:15:48,240 --> 00:15:49,080
Why are you here?

355
00:15:50,560 --> 00:15:51,880
I want to ask you about someone.

356
00:15:53,080 --> 00:15:54,200
Do you know this foreigner?

357
00:15:54,800 --> 00:15:55,880
He said he's a businessman.

358
00:15:57,000 --> 00:15:57,760
Whit Dulant.

359
00:15:58,160 --> 00:15:59,120
He runs a medical company.

360
00:15:59,760 --> 00:16:00,400
He has business

361
00:16:00,560 --> 00:16:02,200
with our company.

362
00:16:03,120 --> 00:16:03,800
Do you remember

363
00:16:03,960 --> 00:16:05,560
I lost my car last time.

364
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:07,400
There was a contract with him in the car.

365
00:16:08,000 --> 00:16:08,600
Why do you ask him?

366
00:16:09,600 --> 00:16:11,440
You should know about Qiu Ya's mom.

367
00:16:11,920 --> 00:16:13,240
She said she took the Restoration Pill.

368
00:16:13,800 --> 00:16:15,800
Manager Cao of the Qiu family bought it.

369
00:16:16,200 --> 00:16:18,000
The seller is Geng Ruilin from the Association.

370
00:16:18,920 --> 00:16:21,600
He has something to do with the Association.

371
00:16:22,120 --> 00:16:24,320
So I want to know his identity.

372
00:16:27,760 --> 00:16:30,160
It seems that he is not an ordinary foreign merchant.
